summaries.short: Following their closely contested loss to the Buccaneers, the Colts enter a December schedule in which every game is crucial.
summaries.full: Following their closely contested loss to the Buccaneers, the Colts enter a December schedule in which every game is crucial. This week, they travel to Houston to play the Texans – a divisional opponent which veteran wideout T.Y. Hilton has tortured during his 10-year Colts career with explosive performances.
